I will be happy this summer, now then you are to be here - and can you help Daddy and me? I'll say you can - and I know you will. 
We must get some sewing done for Hilda, I am hiring Franckie to come and do the part I am not good at, i.e. the cutting and fitting Daddy and I are supposed to leave for Nebraska about the 10th so be sure and get here before that, if possible. But any time you come is O.K. 
Loads and Loads of love
from Mama. 
Tell Amama I'll do what shse says about her clothes - Have not yet received goods and patterns from her 
sent - but it will pass - and I am not complaining for I have few of them now. 
Kiss Amama for me and tell her it surely is wonderful to see the snaps of "our" home and of her standing near it - Is it possible that real people live in such prison houses? Yet one can do a heap of living behind those for-bidding looking walls,... Is that where Jackson used ot be our butter?? and where we lived when these came that terrible blizzard so that the basement was in complete darkness? Ask Amama please for me! Hilda 